1
00:00:12,185 --> 00:00:12,713
How are you feeling?
你感觉怎么样?

2
00:00:13,060 --> 00:00:14,057
Great. Never better.
Great. 从来没这么好过.

3
00:00:14,613 --> 00:00:15,881
Aren't you suffering from jet lag?
难道你没有时差反应?

4
00:00:16,207 --> 00:00:20,154
Oh no.Besides,the afternoon meeting only lasted...What?...four hours?
Oh no.而且,下午的会只开了…… 什么? ……4个小时?

5
00:00:20,377 --> 00:00:22,291
Yes,but we have another one early tomorrow morning.
Yes, 但明天一早我们还有一个会.

6
00:00:22,941 --> 00:00:23,803
It will last all day.
要开一整天.

7
00:00:24,253 --> 00:00:25,976
We won't finish till six o'clock.
我们到晚上6点才能结束.

8
00:00:26,402 --> 00:00:26,660
Hm.
Hm.

9
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:32,102
Are you worried about getting tired?
你会担心很累吗?

10
00:00:32,162 --> 00:00:34,550
No.I wanted to do some shopping tomorrow.
No. 我原打算明天买点儿东西.

11
00:00:34,932 --> 00:00:35,886
How late is Sogo open?
Sogo百货商场开到几点?

12
00:00:36,228 --> 00:00:36,721
Quite late.
相当晚.

13
00:00:37,394 --> 00:00:39,558
But don't forget,there is a banquet for you tomorrow night.
但不要忘了, 明天晚上有欢迎你的宴会.

14
00:00:39,986 --> 00:00:41,198
Ah.How long does that last?
Ah. 那会多久?

15
00:00:41,738 --> 00:00:42,462
They can take hours.
可能要好几个小时.

16
00:00:43,115 --> 00:00:45,785
I'm afraid you won't be back at your hotel at least until midnight.
恐怕你至少也要到半夜才能回饭店.

17
00:00:46,204 --> 00:00:46,442
Maybe later.
也许更晚.

18
00:00:47,217 --> 00:00:47,731
Oh well.
Oh well.

19
00:00:48,199 --> 00:00:51,245
Wait...Sogo's is open tonight,isn't it?
Wait...Sogo今天晚上也开,是吗?

20
00:00:51,681 --> 00:00:51,969
Yes.
Yes.

21
00:00:52,367 --> 00:00:53,440
Well,can we go now?
Well, 我们现在去行吗?

22
00:00:54,830 --> 00:00:57,579
Of course.The tram will take about thirty minutes.
Of course. 乘电车大约30分钟就到了.

23
00:00:58,162 --> 00:00:59,169
A taxi will be faster.
坐出租车去更快.

24
00:00:59,618 --> 00:01:01,341
Let's walk.It's a beautiful evening.
我们步行去吧. 夜色这么好.

25
00:01:01,831 --> 00:01:03,377
I am amazed you're still going!
我太吃惊了, 你还能继续走!

